fnmods_update.title: RGWhatsApp Sudah Terbaru
fnmods_update.description:
Update Now
-Enabled the ability to preview GIF images 
by clicking on them before authorization.
- Enabled the purpose of blocking links. (Settings > 
Privacy > Advanced).
-Many bugs.
-Anti-ban protection.
-Stability and performance improvements.
-More fixes and other improvements.
-More other new features. Enjoy and discover what's 
new for yourself!

Base: 2.24 16.76
